<div class="post_block">
    <h1 style="text-align: center;">Abstract Algorithm</h1>
    <div class="post_info">
        <span class="triangle"></span>
        <span class="hright"></span>

        <p>create possibilities</p>
    </div>

    <p>Hello, I am Dragan Okanovic. I'm a student, vfx programmer and front-end dev. And this is my blog.</p>

    <p>You will find here my experience while working on the projects, thoughts about industry, tutorials, complains about life and some very irrelevant and random stuff as well.</p>

</div>

<div class="post_block half">
    <h1 style="text-align: center;">Recent posts</h1>
    <div class="post_info">
        <span class="triangle"></span>
        <span class="hright"></span>
        <!-- <p>fresh out of the oven</p> -->
    </div>
    <ul>
        [foreach post in 5|Post::recent]
        <li><a href="{CONFIG_WEBSITE}/post/title/{post.link}">{post.title}</a></li>
        [end]
    </ul>
    <p>Search for posts or view the  entire <a href="{CONFIG_WEBSITE}/archive">archive</a>.</p>
</div>

<div class="post_block half">
    <h1 style="text-align: center;">Contact</h1>
    <div class="post_info">
        <span class="triangle"></span>
        <span class="hright"></span>
        <!-- <p>close encounter of the 5th kind</p> -->
    </div>
    
     <p>You can <a href="{CONFIG_WEBSITE}/about#contact">contact</a> me and say hi.<br>Follow me on <a href="https://twitter.com/abstractalgo">Twitter</a>.</p>
